<PB N="xxiii" REF="22">
publicly exhibited. Another hou&s;e haunted, and the gho&s;t di&s;covered. A gho&s;t fond of poultry detected. Sagacious remarks on the &s;ubject. An ho&s;pital haunted.</LABEL>
