<LABEL>LETTER XII. The brothers, &s;i&s;ter, and our hero form an union. Pur|&s;ue their &s;tudies vigorou&s;ly. Their &s;elect and <HI>curious</HI> library. Our hero's lucubrations nearly attended with fatal con&s;equences. His great <HI>talents</HI> for con|trover&s;y duly exhibited</LABEL>
<ITEM>page 90</ITEM>
